OL,9,     Frescue charity. In Marbella, Wenda
OL,10,     Fand her son head to a tattoo
OL,11,     Fparlour.
OL,12,G1000 Nightmare Tenants, Slum Landlords
OL,13,     FAfter moving abroad for work, a
OL,14,     Flandlord discovers that his
OL,15,     Ftenants have left him over 20,000
OL,16,     Fpounds behind with his mortgage.
